\begin{multline}
O(\varepsilon^{2}):\quad0=\bar{D}\varepsilon^{2}\partial_{\bar{t}}\phi_{0}^{out}-\boldsymbol{\bar{\nabla}}^{2}\phi_{0}^{out}+g^{\prime\prime}\left(\phi_{0}^{out}\right)\phi_{2}^{out}+\frac{1}{2}g^{\prime\prime}\left(\phi_{0}^{out}\right)\left(\phi_{1}^{out}\right)^{2}\\
