\begin_layout Standard
Quand on applique cette méthode de correction, le coefficient 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

 dans les équations 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:model_asympt_full_gibbs_+"

\end_inset

 et 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:model_asympt_full_gibbs_-"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

