large
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 interface width, chances are that our model's capillary length is far too
 large.
 This happens mostly if we try to simulate a system in which capillary effects
 are negligible.
 To correct this, we have to remove the implicit excess energy from the
 phase field formulation.
